Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:171504,173339}Oh, Yumemaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:54.84,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:173339,174840}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.88,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:176092,177885}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.93,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:177885,181931}With this little book we'll be able\Nto fulfill any request they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.43,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:178636,181430}Modern Japan\NCompendium of popular songs{NOTE:近代日本\\N歌謡曲全集}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:181931,185518}But I don't know how well\NI can sing in front of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.97,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:185518,186978}You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.60,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:186978,189605}I'll accompany you until\Nyou get used to it. Chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:189605,191983}But what about your\Nevening classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.77,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:191983,193776}What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.15,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:193776,196153}Our school's idol is making\Nher debut in the showbiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.11,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:196153,199115}I can always study some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:199115,200616}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.07,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:200616,202076}Alright, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.82,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:202076,204829}We've got to find a nice place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.53,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:204829,206539}Hmm… How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:206539,208583}I guess that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:30.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:208583,210626}Alright, I'll try going in by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.29,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:210626,212295}That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:34.46,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:213629,214463}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:224098,225808}How about a song, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:46.55,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:225808,226559}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.35,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:228227,231355}Whoa, what a cute girl.\NCome, sit with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:231355,233899}Stop it, please.\NGet your hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.40,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:233899,236402}Oh, don't be like that.\NI'll buy you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:236402,237778}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:242366,244535}This is why I hate drunkards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.70,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:244535,246704}But we'll get nowhere\Nif you're like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:246704,247872}Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.79,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:247872,250791}Alright, let me handle it.\NI'll pick a customer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.46,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:250791,253461}What? A traveling singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.46,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:253461,256464}Yes, it's a special discount. For just\N100 yen, she'll sing two songs for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.79,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:256464,258799}Alright. Then have her sing\N"Ballad About The Captain".{NOTE:船頭小唄\\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.71,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:258799,260718}B-"Ballad About The Captain"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.51,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:261469,262511}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:26.18,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:262511,266182}The heck you doing?\NShe doesn't know how to sing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.51,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:266182,267516}I'm sorry.\NWe'll find it in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.72,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:267516,269727}Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.06,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:269727,271062}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.56,Default,Drunkard,0,0,0,,{TIME:271062,273564}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.73,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:276817,281739}Looks like if you want to succeed,\Nyou'll have to know half of this book by heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:281739,284075}I don't have time to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:47.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:284075,287203}I have to make money as fast\Nas possible. It can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.24,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:287203,290247}You're right.\NYour dad's still in the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:55.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:290247,295628}Yes, unfortunately. I'm sure I can\Nmake money singing the songs I know.
