Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:323322,324490}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:28.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:324490,328035}I'm a new singer on the block.\NTonight I'd like to try to perform for you.
