Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:334959,336627}What a good girl you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:40.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:336627,340047}Really, you're so sweet\Nit crushes my heart, Nozomi-chan.
