Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:50.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:404445,410868}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  My life's getting dark.  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:私の人生暗かった}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:57.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:410868,417208}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  No matter how dark the past,  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:過去はどんなに暗くとも}
