Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:430888,432473}W-Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:16.51,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:432473,436519}Man, you really\Nare something! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:457832,460209}That's right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:460209,461752}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:461752,463128}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.54,Default,Customers,0,0,0,,{TIME:463128,464547}– Encore!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.50,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:464547,466507}Took the words out of my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.00,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:466507,469009}But before asking for encore,\Nshow a token of appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.38,Default,Customers,0,0,0,,{TIME:469009,470386}Y-Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.63,Default,Customers,0,0,0,,{TIME:470386,473639}Alright. Good.\NMore, more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.97,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:476475,478978}Do not hesitate. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.02,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:478978,480020}Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.31,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:480020,481313}How about you, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.98,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:481313,482982}That's it. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:482982,485818}Really, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:487444,489071}Take a look. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.90,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:489071,492908}I can't believe you managed to collect\Nso much money by singing in bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:492908,496287}If I manage to earn this much every night,\NDad's hospitalization shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.62,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:496287,499623}I'm sorry you have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:499623,501333}Mom, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:501333,502960}I love singing.\NIt's not a chore at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:26.00,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:502960,506005}If we had known that something\Nlike this would happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.75,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:506005,509758}we wouldn't have given up your\Nolder brother for adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:509758,511218}Let's not talk about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:511218,514138}What's done is done.\NIt's no use crying over spilled milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.55,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:514138,516557}I'm sorry.\NI'm an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:527526,529153}{\i1}My brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:533157,535868}{\i1}I'd like to meet him some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.79,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:544460,546795}Hey. Mine. Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:546795,549131}Yes sir. What do you want me to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.72,Default,Kōda Miki's follower A,0,0,0,,{TIME:550966,554720}That's how you end up when you\Nhit bars at night: with a huge hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.34,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:555346,557348}I heard your dream\Nis to become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.80,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:557348,560809}I understand you have to work.\NJust make sure you don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:560809,562811}Yes sir. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.94,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,{TIME:562811,566941}As for punishment, you'll sing\Nsomething for us during the break.{NOTE:罰として 休み時間に 曲 サービスするんだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:566941,568067}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.48,Default,Students,0,0,0,,{TIME:568067,570486}– Good for you!\N– Way to go, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:572905,573906}{\i1}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:38.45,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:573906,578452}{\i1}They're like, "Nozomi, Nozomi", but they\Njust show her sympathy because she's poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:47.00,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:578452,587002}{NOTE:越後屋\\N大象酒場}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.92,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:591131,592925}{\i1}What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.80,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:592925,595803}{\i1}Mine Nozomi is getting popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:06.31,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:599139,606313}{\i1}I wanted her to taste the sufferings\Nand misfortunes of poverty as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:14.32,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:607982,614321}{\i1}That's why I switched the babies 17 years ago.\NBut if it goes on like this, it's all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:25.70,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:619618,625708}{\i1}Mine Nozomi. You were born to an important family,\Nbut you were raised by very poor parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.54,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:625708,629545}{\i1}You should suffer more, much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.25,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:630921,632256}{\i1}Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.80,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:632256,635801}{\i1}Everything will come in time.
