Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:639263,641690}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.19,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:648856,651191}Hey, girl. So it's you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.69,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:651191,653694}The new traveling singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:654987,657156}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:01.36,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:657156,661368}You don't know? This is our territory.\NWe're the Kashima Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:661368,662745}Your territory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.74,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:662745,665748}Yes. You forgot to come and say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.91,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:665748,667916}Say hello? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.96,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:667916,670961}You're making money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:670961,673380}Why do I have to respond\Nto your questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.84,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:673380,674840}Listen here, you snot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.63,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:674840,677634}Do you even realize\Nthe trouble you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:677634,679344}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.51,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:682848,684516}Wait! What are you doing\Nto Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.47,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:684516,686477}Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:686477,687770}Yumemaro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.85,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:687770,689855}Alright, that's it. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:35.61,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:692399,695611}This is bad. I need to find help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.98,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:696403,697988}I'll cut to the chase, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:42.99,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:697988,702993}Because of you, other singers'\Nearnings are going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:702993,704244}Other singers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:48.41,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:704244,708415}Yes. We can do this the easy way.\NYou just have to settle your debt to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:708415,709708}A debt to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.79,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:709708,712795}Just pay us what we had lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:712795,716465}No way. Why do I have\Nto give money to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.96,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:716465,717966}You've asked for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:719676,721220}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.43,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:721220,724431}Hey! Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.89,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:724431,726892}Three grown men against one girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:11.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:726892,731480}If you have something against her, you'll have\Nto talk to me, the great Kuma-san, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.64,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:731480,732648}So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:732648,734399}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.82,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:737111,738821}Hold on. We can talk. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.78,Default,Takada Yumemaro,0,0,0,,{TIME:740405,741782}Show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:760676,762094}{\i1}The guitar…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:763262,764346}{\i1}The guitar…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:767141,768934}{\i1}My guitar…
Comment: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:51.38,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:771386,771386}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:54.33,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:771745,774331}I won't talk to you small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:13:00.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:774331,780170}Until you get your boss' ass in here,\NI refuse to move an inch from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.38,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:780170,782381}That's a nice tattoo, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.46,Default,Yakuza,0,0,0,,{TIME:782381,785467}But we don't put tattoos\Non our backs anymore these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.59,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:785467,787594}Yeah, that's not the only thing\Nthat has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.76,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:787594,791765}Yakuza now is completely different\Nfrom what it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:16.77,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:791765,796770}Listen. I think you're having a wrong idea\Nabout what Nozomi-chan is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.18,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:797771,799189}Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:24.77,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:800357,804778}She's poorer than a church mouse,\Nyet she takes care of her dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:29.15,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:804778,809158}tries to support her family however she can\Nand looks after her younger siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.70,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:809158,812703}She started singing to earn money\Nfor her father's hospitalization fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.82,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:812703,813829}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:813829,815622}Why do you bully this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.12,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:815622,817124}Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:817124,818625}Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.08,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:818625,822087}Now until you fix this thing for her\Nthat your thugs broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.46,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:822087,824464}I won't budge an inch from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.63,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:824464,825632}Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:828093,830345}That's more or less how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:53.34,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:830345,833348}So cool! Uncle, you're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:55.35,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:833348,835350}A-Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:58.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:835350,838478}Don't you worry, Nozomi-chan.\NYou can work tonight wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:838478,840981}Yeah. Thanks. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.10,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:840981,844109}They won't lay a finger on you\Nanymore, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844109,846403}No. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:846403,849907}They got me to think. If I keep singing,\NI'll make other singers lose money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.03,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:849907,853035}I'm not surprised. You're too nice\Nfor your own good, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:16.45,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:853035,856455}But you shouldn't worry.\NJust sing from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.24,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:856455,859249}Don't let anybody\Nhold you back, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:859249,861251}Maybe. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.58,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:861251,863587}Is our girl really so talented?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.79,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:863587,864796}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:26.96,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:864796,866965}That's the last thing\Nyou need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.76,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:866965,869760}Everyone says she\Nshould become a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:872888,874848}Exaggerating as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:40.06,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:874848,880062}No, it's the truth. They say you're so good\Nyou can really become a professional singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:880062,880854}A professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.77,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:880854,881772}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.40,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:881772,885400}That's great. If you sign a contract,\Nyou'll make tons of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.94,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:885400,887945}Wow! Sis, you'll be in TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887945,889446}Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.11,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:890614,893116}You'd need to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:56.53,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:893116,896536}Kuma-san, be careful not to give\NNozomi any false hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:01.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:896536,901625}No, even Fuji Keiko and Kitajima Sabu-chan\Nhad to start off somewhere.{NOTE:藤圭子\\N北島のサブちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:901625,903627}Should I introduce you\Nto a good teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:903627,905504}Stop it. These jokes are going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.71,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:906380,910717}I may not look like it, but I worked\Nin the recording industry in my younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.09,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:910717,913095}I can tell a word to a person or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:913095,914721}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.18,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:914721,916181}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:916181,918809}Do not hesitate to call me\Nif you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.06,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:918809,920060}Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:920060,921395}Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:921395,923814}Nozomi-chan, you have it in you.\NI know you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:937953,941623}{\i1}If it really is possible, I'd like\Nto build my life with the songs I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:941623,945043}{\i1}I'd be able to get out of poverty\Nand maybe even meet my brother in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.67,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:947421,950674}{\i1}But is it really going to be so easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.59,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:952175,954594}Rookie of the Year Final Battle\NFanni Moriyama{NOTE:オール日本新人王\\N決定戦\\Nファニー森山}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:957139,960142}{\i1}"The decisive match for the\NRookie of the Year boxing title".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:960142,962894}{\i1}Fanni Moriyama\Nand Condor Nakagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:963562,965439}Fanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:965439,967399}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:969735,971403}{\i1}So you were a boxer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:973822,974698}{\i1}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.15,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:975991,977159}Keep your legs working, Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:18.99,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:977159,978994}Come on, Hoshiyama.\NYou can do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.20,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:978994,980203}Don't escape from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.16,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:980203,982164}Barrage, barrage!\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.70,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:982164,983707}Evade! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.08,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:983707,985083}Left! Behind his guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.79,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:985083,986793}Fanni! You're awfully slow today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.87,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:986793,988879}Come on, show me your usual speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.88,Default,Coach,0,0,0,,{TIME:988879,990881}Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:994384,996428}I'm sorry for interrupting your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.13,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:996428,998138}No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:999139,1002809}I wanted to thank you for donating your blood\Nto my father. It was very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:46.60,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002809,1006605}Anyone would've done the same thing.\NI only happened to be there at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007439,1009149}Yes, but thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010150,1013070}I bet you were surprised\Nwhen you learned that I'm boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013070,1016198}Yes, especially after I had seen\Nyou driving that expensive car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016198,1017783}Uhm, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.07,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019618,1022079}I decided to devote\Nall my time to boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023914,1026375}At least while I'm still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:09.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026375,1029711}It's very nice to be able to do\Nwhat you really like in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.29,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029711,1031296}You have your music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:17.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033423,1037219}Yes. But I can't decide\Nif I should become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.55,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037219,1038553}Become a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.59,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038553,1041598}That's a great idea!\NYou'd make a very fine singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041598,1044434}But it's going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.39,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045977,1048397}Yeah, I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.31,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048397,1050315}But still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.06,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050315,1053068}You can't do anything\Nif you're afraid of the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054653,1056613}I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:41.41,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056613,1061410}I'm in the same boat as you. I don't know\Nif I can win the title of the Rookie of the Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061410,1064371}I've got to take a shot at it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064371,1066206}You're right. I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066206,1067374}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.91,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067374,1068917}You want to become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:49.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068917,1069709}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069709,1070794}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.62,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070794,1072629}Then just become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072629,1074214}Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.84,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074214,1076842}Yes. Give it a shot\Nthe best way you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076842,1078301}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.01,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078301,1081012}That's right. You'll succeed, or…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081012,1082973}Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.30,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082973,1085308}You'll spend your life\Nsinging in bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.69,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090188,1091690}Alright, it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091690,1093692}I'll take a shot at this, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119718,1120802}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:47.26,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124556,1127267}{\i1}Do you remember me, Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.26,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127267,1129269}{\i1}You remember my voice, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130270,1132022}– It's you again.\N– {\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:55.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132022,1135734}Quiet. Every time you call me,\Nsomething unpleasant happens after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135734,1138278}Stop it already.\NWhy are you so persistent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.65,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141364,1144659}{\i1}Is that how you speak to someone who has\Nspared you the sufferings of poverty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.91,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144659,1146912}{\i1}and gave you the life of\Na rich heiress you have now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146912,1149956}What is it that you want?\NIs it money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.70,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149956,1151708}You'll know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:15.54,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151708,1155545}Are you aware that Mine Nozomi has\Ndecided to become a professional singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:18.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155545,1158381}{\i1}What does it have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.75,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158381,1160759}I guess not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:26.30,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160759,1166306}But if Mine Nozomi becomes a big star,\Nshe'll look down on you. You'll be a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.43,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167182,1170435}{\i1}Are you telling me\Nit won't hurt your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171853,1173605}She really is doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.02,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173605,1175023}{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.23,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175023,1178235}{\i1}I've always been your ally\Nsince the day of your birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.65,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178235,1180654}{\i1}This is why I don't want to\Nsee you lose to Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:44.57,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183907,1184574}{\i1}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184574,1186076}W-Wait, don't hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186076,1189496}If you really are my ally,\Nyou can meet me in person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.91,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189496,1190914}I'd like to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:51.87,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190914,1191873}Meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.62,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191873,1193625}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:57.12,Default,Nohara Michiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193625,1197128}Very well. Come to Club Amour\Naround 8 o'clock tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.85,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1208390,1210850}Club Amour{NOTE:クラブアムール}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.85,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214396,1215855}Good evening.{NOTE:いらっしゃいません}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220193,1222070}{\i1}She was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212761,1215855}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  …tell me everything  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:すべてを打ち明けて}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:22.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215855,1222195}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm enchanted, I'm suffering,  {\fnArial}♪\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  but I'm not moving from here for you  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:恋をして 苦しんで 来た私だけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:29.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222195,1229119}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm tired of this,  {\fnArial}♪\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  let me grow up already  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:もういやなの 卒業させてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:36.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229119,1236334}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm the one who has asked you  {\fnArial}♪\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  for this dream in the first place  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:あなたにその夢を 求めた私}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:45.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236334,1245760}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  You're a man just like the others,  {\fnArial}♪\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  yet there's something different about you  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:おんなじ男でも あなたは違う}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:52.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245760,1252726}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm in despair, I'm heartbroken  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  and I have given up my hope  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:恋に泣き 愛にゆれ そして諦めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:59.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252726,1259232}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm biting my lips, enduring things,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  but I'm not moving from here for you  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:唇を噛み締めて 来た私だけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:04.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259232,1264946}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm tired of this,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  let me grow up already  {\fnArial}♪{NOTE:もういやなの 卒業させてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:15.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274164,1275423}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:27.05,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1278418,1287052}Club Amour · Staff Entrance{NOTE:通用口}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279669,1281046}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281046,1282464}Let me sing for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.84,Default,Waiter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282464,1283840}Sure. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283840,1285592}I will. Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293141,1294726}Oh, Kōda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294726,1296978}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.22,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296978,1298229}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:40.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298229,1300106}I know you're in cahoots\Nwith the woman on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300106,1301566}What woman on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301566,1302484}What cahoots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.02,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302484,1305028}I can't believe\Nhow presumptuous you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:48.94,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305028,1308948}The woman whom you asked to invite me\Nhere to show off your popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308948,1310950}Do you really want\Nto boast so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310950,1313203}What on earth\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:57.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313203,1317165}You make me pity you. You think you'll move me\Nwith your amateur singing in some bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:58.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317165,1318625}Kōda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:02.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318625,1322712}But it's fine. If you want to become\Na professional singer, feel free to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322712,1324923}Who told you that I wanted\Nto become a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:08.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324923,1328468}But I strongly advise you to stop\Ncalling me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:13.13,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328468,1333139}Because if you don't,\NI have an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:17.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333139,1337936}Again about that phone?\NI'm sorry, but you're not making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:19.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337936,1339729}Drop the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:23.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339729,1343566}Kōda-san, I think\Nit's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343566,1345985}No, it's not a misunderstanding.\NIt's the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345985,1347904}I can see it very well\Nfrom the look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.69,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347904,1349698}But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:32.65,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349698,1352659}Go, become a professional\Nsinger if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:35.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352659,1355495}You'll still end up\Nprostrating yourself at my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.29,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357372,1359290}Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359290,1362168}Mine-san, I'm going to\Nbecome a singer as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:43.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362168,1363753}But I will be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363753,1366047}A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:48.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366047,1368883}I won't lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:52.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368883,1372887}I don't understand, but apparently it's no use\Ntrying to make this a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.43,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372887,1375432}Heh. You barely make ends meet.\NWhat can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:58.35,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375432,1378351}Soon you will bow down to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:02.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380770,1382147}Mark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:05.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382147,1385859}When I want something, I always have my way,\Nwith Daddy's help if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:15.70,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1392574,1395702}{\i1}Kōda Miki openly declares to\Nbecome a professional singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:19.91,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395702,1399914}{\i1}Mine Nozomi secretly\Ndesires the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:24.87,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399914,1404878}{\i1}This was the fateful moment when\Nthe rivalry between the two was born.
