Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:38.08,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414287,1418083}{\i1}One day, Kumagorō brings\Na news that raises Nozomi's hopes:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:43.58,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418083,1423588}{\i1}A popular composer, Egawa Isao,\Nis said to appear often in a nearby bar.
